  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  On HD three times a week for more than 3 months (minimizing the confounding effects of
             residual renal function)

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Malignancy;

          -  Obvious infections or inflammatory diseases;

          -  Preexisting haematological disorders; and,

          -  Clinically significant bleeding, transfusion, hospitalization, surgery, or renal
             transplantation
      </textblock>
